        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.25911v1",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-28T17:55:49Z",
        "description": "Multi-wavelength observations of molecular and ionized gas indicate that GMCs are short-lived, generally dispersing within one or two dynamical timescales. To investigate the physical origin of these short lifetimes and the role of star formation prescriptions, we conduct radiation-hydrodynamic simu",
        "title_cn": "从短寿命到长寿命云： NGC 300类星系模拟中恒星形成模型对巨型分子云演化的影响"
      },
      {
