        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.25903v1",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-28T17:48:16Z",
        "description": "The accelerating adoption of Large Language Models (LLMs) in software engineering (SE) has brought with it a silent crisis: unsustainable computational cost. While these models demonstrate remarkable capabilities in different SE tasks, they are unmanageably large, slow to deploy, memory-intensive, a",
        "title_cn": "碳税变压器：过度生长的语言模型的绿色压缩管道"
      },
