        "description": "This is Paper 6 of a series of formally-verified analyses of masked NTT hardware for post-quantum cryptography; Paper 1 [1] established structural dependency analysis of the QANARY platform, and Paper 2 [2] quantified security margins under partial NTT masking. Boolean masking composition is well-un",
        "title_cn": "素场PINI ：后量子NTT掩蔽的机器检查组成定理"
      },
      {
